      "span_text": "A similar trend was observed in a survey of more than 300 residences in Poland by [CITATION_1] and in a study of 709 New Jersey homes by Klotz and colleagues (1993) where the average of four-day winter basement radon measurements also overestimated their corresponding annual average basement radon concentrations by 34 and 8 Bq m −3 , respectively.",
